# ğŸ½ï¸ SmartMenu QR

A **QR-codeâ€“based Smart Menu Food Ordering System** designed for restaurants and hotels. Customers scan a QR code to view the menu and place orders, while admins manage menu items, availability, and orders through a secure dashboard.

This system is built with **simplicity, scalability, and real-world restaurant workflows** in mind.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

### ğŸ‘¤ Customer Side

* Scan QR code to access menu (no app install required)
* View food items with price, description, and availability
* Place orders directly from the menu
* Works well on mobile devices

### ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’¼ Admin / Kitchen Side

* Secure admin dashboard
* Add, edit, delete, and copy menu items
* Control food availability (Available / Out of Stock)
* Manage categories and pricing
* Real-time order visibility for kitchen staff

