## ğŸ§± Database Design (Core Tables)

### `menu_items`

| Column       | Type      | Description             |
| ------------ | --------- | ----------------------- |
| id           | INT       | Primary Key             |
| name         | VARCHAR   | Food name               |
| description  | TEXT      | Food description        |
| price        | DECIMAL   | Food price              |
| category     | VARCHAR   | Food category           |
| stock        | INT       | Quantity                |
| availability | BOOLEAN   | Available / Unavailable |
| created_at   | TIMESTAMP | Record creation time    |

### `orders`

| Column     | Type      | Description                  |
| ---------- | --------- | ---------------------------- |
| id         | INT       | Primary Key                  |
| table_no   | VARCHAR   | Table identifier             |
| status     | VARCHAR   | pending / preparing / served |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Order time                   |

