## âš™ï¸ Installation & Setup

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Prerequisites

* XAMPP or LAMP stack
* PHP 8+
* MySQL 5.7+

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/smartmenu-qr.git
```

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Database Setup

* Create a database named `smartmenu`
* Import `database/smartmenu.sql`

### 4ï¸âƒ£ Configure Database

Edit `includes/db.php`:

```php
$host = 'localhost';
$user = 'root';
$pass = '';
$db   = 'smartmenu';
```

### 5ï¸âƒ£ Run the Project

* Start Apache & MySQL
* Open in browser:

```
http://localhost/smartmenu-qr/
```

